  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together semolina, sugar, and salt.",
    "Add unsalted butter, milk, rose water, and orange zest to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Place the fish fillets in a separate bowl and coat with the semolina mixture.",
    "Fold the fish fillets in half and place them in a baking dish.",
    "Sprinkle pine nuts over the top of the fish.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the fish is cooked through.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
  ],
